  "title": "Occurrence of New Characteristics in Chickpea — Purplish Stem with White Flowers",
  "abstract": "A natural mutant which combines purplish stems with white flowers was identified. This trait combination is not previously known in Cicer. Data on 9 yield components are tabulated for both the mutant chickpea (designated ICC17101) and cv. Annigeri grown during 1996-97.",
